### ===========================================
### Face Recognition API - Authentication
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension
### ===========================================

@baseUrl = http://{{$dotenv API_HOST}}:{{$dotenv API_PORT}}


### ===========================================
### Health Check
### ===========================================

### Server health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/


### ===========================================
### Authentication
### ===========================================

### Register new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "password": "test0123"
}

###

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "password": "test0123"
}
